Title: Authorizes private membership establishments to have certain licenses for sale of alcohol
Summary: Authorizes private membership establishments to have certain licenses for sale of alcohol for consumption on premises.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to establishing a license to sell liquor on premises commonly known as a for-profit club
